      "message": "Yeah I think each layer of this needs to be type alias\u0027ed.  At least one of those reasons is because Console groups have titles.  So I\u0027d probably embed the groups and do something like this:\n\ntype ConsoleSummary {\n  Name *Link  // Links to the console.\n  []model.BuilderSummary\n}\n\ntype ConsoleGroup struct {\n  Config config.ConsoleSummaryGroup  // This probably isn\u0027t necessary\n  Title *Link  // Provided by the config above\n  Consoles []ConsoleSummary\n}\n\nConsoleHeader struct {\n  ConsoleGroups []ConsoleGroup\n}",
